			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><b><a href="http://www.zumsteg.net">By Derek Zumsteg.</a></b><br />
Read by Jared Axelrod (of <a href="http://www.publicwords.org">The Department of Public Words</a>).<br /></p>

<p><i>&#8220;I read an interesting forum post last night,&#8221; my electric toothbrush told me over its low burr.</i></p>

